{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "7c3a9e21-f4b5-4d8a-bc12-3e9f0a1b2c3d",
    "name": "Voz Ciudadana — Backend API",
    "description": "Colección completa de la API REST del backend de Voz Ciudadana.\n\n**Flujo recomendado:**\n1. Ejecutar `POST /auth/login` → extrae `access_token`, `refresh_token` y `user_id` automáticamente.\n2. El resto de requests usan `Bearer {{access_token}}` heredado de la colección.\n3. El pre-request script de colección renueva el `access_token` automáticamente cuando expira (≤60s).\n\n**Roles disponibles:** `SUPERADMIN` · `COORDINADOR` · `OPERADOR_CHAT` · `ANALISTA`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{access_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "id": "col-prerequest-autorefresh",
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// ── Auto-refresh del access token ──────────────────────────────────",
          "// Se ejecuta antes de CADA request de la colección.",
          "// Si el token está a ≤60s de expirar, lo renueva transparentemente.",
          "const accessToken = pm.environment.get('access_token');",
          "const refreshToken = pm.environment.get('refresh_token');",
          "",
          "if (!accessToken || !refreshToken) { return; }",
          "",
          "let payload;",
          "try {",
          "  payload = JSON.parse(atob(accessToken.split('.')[1]));",
          "} catch (e) { return; }",
          "",
          "const expiresAt = (payload.exp || 0) * 1000;",
          "const bufferMs = 60 * 1000; // 60s de margen antes de expirar",
          "",
          "if (Date.now() + bufferMs < expiresAt) { return; }",
          "",
          "const baseUrl = pm.environment.get('base_url') || 'http://localhost:8000';",
          "const deviceId = pm.environment.get('device_id') || 'postman-default';",
          "",
          "pm.sendRequest(",
          "  {",
          "    url: `${baseUrl}/api/v1/auth/refresh`,",
          "    method: 'POST',",
          "    header: [",
          "      { key: 'Content-Type', value: 'application/json' },",
          "      { key: 'x-device-id', value: deviceId }",
          "    ],",
          "    body: {",
          "      mode: 'raw',",
          "      raw: JSON.stringify({ refreshToken, deviceId })",
          "    }",
          "  },",
          "  (err, res) => {",
          "    if (err) { console.error('[Auto-Refresh] Error:', err); return; }",
          "    if (res.code !== 200) { console.warn('[Auto-Refresh] Failed HTTP:', res.code); return; }",
          "    const json = res.json();",
          "    pm.environment.set('access_token', json.accessToken);",
          "    pm.environment.set('refresh_token', json.refreshToken);",
          "    console.log('[Auto-Refresh] Tokens renovados correctamente');",
          "  }",
          ");"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
